"Change your life and start learning today by activating your {platform_name}"
" account. Click on the link below or copy and paste it into your browser's "
"address bar."
msgstr ""
"Canvia la teva vida i comença a aprendre avui activant el teu compte "
"{platform_name}. Clica l'enllaç de sota o copia'l i enganxa'l a la barra "
